Ophelia Lovibond https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ophelia_Lovibond 0 Ophelia Lucy Lovibond (born 19 February 1986) is an English actress. She is known for her roles as Carina in the film Guardians of the Galaxy and as Izzy Gould in the BBC's W1A. Ophelia_Lucy_Lovibond ( born 19_February_1986 ) is an_English_actress .
